Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:18.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}視界に目前映る深い真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:28.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}この先およそ 40000km
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:35.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}後ろに迫る互いの傷が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:40.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}迷う道をさらに迷わせてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:45.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}見えず匂わぬ、違えぬ未来が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:47.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}背中を突いた！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:48.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:57.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}今日の夜は隣にいさせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:06.03,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}今夜だけは本気だからね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:09.74,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}こっちにきてもっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:12.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}祈りあった未来とて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:14.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}道が違うのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:15.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}アナタ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.25,0:23:21.63,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}互いの殺意で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:25.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}トドメ喰らっちゃうね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.43,0:23:29.64,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}やっぱりやめとくわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:18.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}映入视野的深邃绯红
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:28.24,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}前方大约还有40000km
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:35.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}紧追过来的彼此的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:40.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}让迷茫的路途再添迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:45.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}不可视不可闻的唯一未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:47.47,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}从背后一击！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:48.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:57.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}今夜请让我伴你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:06.03,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}只有今夜我无比认真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:09.74,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}再靠过来一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:12.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}纵然我们一同祈愿的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:14.04,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}前路也会分岔而行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:15.87,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.25,0:23:21.63,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}让我们倾尽彼此的杀意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:25.01,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}给予对方最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.43,0:23:29.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}果然还是算了吧
